Rating, 5 stars,  · September 2023,  · Stayed over a week
rating_comment: Great value for money! Situated in a calm and relaxed area of Banani, within walking distance to many shops, restaurants etc. We stayed there for two weeks, and I'll definitely rent this apartment again when visiting Dhaka 👌 The owner replied within a few minutes and his caretaker lived next door, so every time we asked for fresh towels, cleaning etc. it was fixed really fast 😊

info: Rating, 5 stars,  · September 2023,  · Stayed a few nights
rating_comment:
We found the place very quickly, due to a good description. A really nicely decorated home, with all you need for cooking, microwave oven, fridge and water dispenser 😊 Pretty clean I'd say. I found it noisy at first, but it's just how this city is I'm afraid. The apartment is about 10 minutes walk away from an even busier/noisier area, so that's a relief.
The host replied within minutes every time we asked for something, and was very helpful! Appreciate that 😊
